data.description: Calling all investors!  Welcome to your new home nestled in the heart of a serene cul-de-sac, just minutes away from the bustling Medical Center area. This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts a generous 1,594 sq ft of living space, situated in an established neighborhood adorned with towering trees that provide a picturesque backdrop. Although this home is in need of some tender loving care (TLC), its potential shines through, offering a unique opportunity to customize and transform it into your dream haven. The property is priced accordingly, providing a fantastic investment for those looking to add their personal touch and create lasting memories in a desirable location. Step outside into the backyard oasis, where you'll find a refreshing pool, a covered patio perfect for outdoor entertaining, and a privacy fence that provides seclusion. Imagine lazy afternoons by the pool or hosting gatherings with friends and family in the privacy of your own outdoor retreat. Please note that the pool has been drained, providing a blank canvas for your creative vision. Convenience meets tranquility in this ideally located home, where the proximity to the Medical Center ensures easy access to work, healthcare, and various amenities. Take advantage of the charm of an established neighborhood while enjoying the potential for modern upgrades.
